# ── Vivado generated project ────────────────────────────────────────────
# The whole Vivado project is reproducible from scripts/create_project.tcl,
# so none of it belongs in version control. Ignore everything under vivado/
# except the build script(s) that live there.
vivado/*
!vivado/.gitkeep

# ── Vivado junk that can appear anywhere ────────────────────────────────
*.jou
*.log
*.str
*.pb
*.dcp
*.bit
*.ltx
.Xil/
vivado*.backup.*
usage_statistics_webtalk.*

# ── Editor / OS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
*.swp
*~
.DS_Store
